Did you know more than 140,000 elephants have disappeared from the African Savanna in the last decade? #KnotOnMyPlanet and definitely not in the next decade 🚫🚫 Since 2017, @TiffanyAndCo has raised over $5 Million for the Wildlife Conservation to fight against anti-poaching, anti-trafficking, and ivory demand. Join me and @TiffanyandCo to support this amazing initiative @elephantcrisisfund where all proceeds go towards keeping these beautiful animals alive. 🐘 🌎 
#TiffanySaveTheWild

Feeling very very very grateful for all of your support this year on the podcast and wanted to send a big thank you to everyone who’s tuned in! And the biggest thank you to those who have come on the show, lent their voice, and let me interrogate them for a few hours 🗣😉 Here’s to more spaces where people feel comfortable and safe to share their stories, inspire others, and be themselves in 2020 ❤️🤞🏼🎙🙏🏼
📸 @cibellelevi

Got to spend Tuesday night at the @toryburch store hosting my closest friends and family, celebrating the holidays, and raising awareness for @makeawishamerica. I’m constantly in awe of the way that Tory and her team navigate the fashion industry - creating beautiful collections and always finding a way to give back to their community and causes around the world.  Thank you for always setting the bar high, for letting me turn your store into my living room for a few hours, and to everyone who came out and supported ❤️
PS: I added in a swipe up in my stories for those who couldn’t make it and want to make a donation!
#torystories

@alyssainthecity is one of my closest friends and someone who I frequently turn to for career advice, so I really love how candid and personal this interview was. This was one of my favorite things she said ❤️
We also talk about:
- Making the move from corporate to freelance
- The influencer stigma and finding identity in the fashion industry
- Growing your network in a meaningful way and fostering real relationships
- Managing the balance between creativity and efficiency
- How working with women has shaped her career
- And just us being us 😉🗣
Link in bio. Enjoy! 🎙

Good morning some PSAs🚨‼️
1. There’s a new episode of the podcast out with @alyssainthecity! It’s one of the last episodes of the year and I’m so grateful for all of your support and love on this project.
2. In the episode, I give all the juicy details on a holiday party I’m hosting with @toryburch at their Rodeo Dr. store in LA 🎄🎁 We’ll be monogramming sweaters, painting on bags, and doing everything you need to win best gift giver this year, with proceeds from the night going to @makeawishamerica ❤️ More details at the beginning of the episode and you can DM me to RSVP.
Thanks for listening and have a nice day ☀️‼️
📸 by @cibellelevi

Ever walked down the street and seen an outfit so good you spend hours on google trying to find the exact look? Same….. So excited to be partnering with @Uniqlo for the launch of @StyleHint_Official, a new style search engine that allows you to search new styles with just one snap. Just take a photo and the app will automatically populate options of the look. Over the next few months I’ll be showing you how to use the app, behind-the-scenes of some of my everyday outfits, and how you can find new style inspiration from around the world #uniqlo #stylehint #ad
